  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a small indie team,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An action-sports game where size matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play against your friends, locally and online in explosive team-based sports matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can change sizes at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small = Fast</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Large = Strong</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium = Balanced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shrink and grow to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/172b3a59f855b163b206f203790326c5.avif?t=1742297907\" width=607 height=75 /></span>-<strong>This Game is in EARLY ACCESS (Game Preview) and in active development, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Full release (with full features) are planned by <strong>2026.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-View our roadmap (below) for more details!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/2edf772af83240c9a8fb779be41738b9.avif?t=1742297907\" width=607 height=75 /></span>1) Hit the Ball Into The Other Team's Net To Score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/1e84316f84d576918bbeb381aeb1c0b6.poster.avif?t=1742297907\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/1e84316f84d576918bbeb381aeb1c0b6.webm?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/1e84316f84d576918bbeb381aeb1c0b6.mp4?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) First Team to 10 Points Wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/824d93cf7f1245a48ac0a14fee9bedc2.poster.avif?t=1742297907\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/824d93cf7f1245a48ac0a14fee9bedc2.webm?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/824d93cf7f1245a48ac0a14fee9bedc2.mp4?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3) Swap between 3 sizes anytime:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Small = Speed, Medium = Balanced, Mega = Power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/6b6b62be3ecdf14abcf9cd52f47d16e0.poster.avif?t=1742297907\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/6b6b62be3ecdf14abcf9cd52f47d16e0.webm?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/6b6b62be3ecdf14abcf9cd52f47d16e0.mp4?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the 3 styles to your advantage to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roadmap last updated April 17, 2023</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks and have fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Dave & The Rise and Fall Team</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a small indie team,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An action-sports game where size matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play against your friends, locally and online in explosive team-based sports matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can change sizes at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small = Fast</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Large = Strong</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium = Balanced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shrink and grow to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/172b3a59f855b163b206f203790326c5.avif?t=1742297907\" width=607 height=75 /></span>-<strong>This Game is in EARLY ACCESS (Game Preview) and in active development, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Full release (with full features) are planned by <strong>2026.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-View our roadmap (below) for more details!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/2edf772af83240c9a8fb779be41738b9.avif?t=1742297907\" width=607 height=75 /></span>1) Hit the Ball Into The Other Team's Net To Score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/1e84316f84d576918bbeb381aeb1c0b6.poster.avif?t=1742297907\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/1e84316f84d576918bbeb381aeb1c0b6.webm?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/1e84316f84d576918bbeb381aeb1c0b6.mp4?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) First Team to 10 Points Wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/824d93cf7f1245a48ac0a14fee9bedc2.poster.avif?t=1742297907\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/824d93cf7f1245a48ac0a14fee9bedc2.webm?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/824d93cf7f1245a48ac0a14fee9bedc2.mp4?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3) Swap between 3 sizes anytime:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Small = Speed, Medium = Balanced, Mega = Power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/6b6b62be3ecdf14abcf9cd52f47d16e0.poster.avif?t=1742297907\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/6b6b62be3ecdf14abcf9cd52f47d16e0.webm?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332840/extras/6b6b62be3ecdf14abcf9cd52f47d16e0.mp4?t=1742297907\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the 3 styles to your advantage to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roadmap last updated April 17, 2023</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"